Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning.listener

Interface EnrollingServiceListener

public interface EnrollingServiceListener
This interface will allow the mobile wallet to understand the current stage of the enrollment process.
See Also:
com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.utils.securekeypad.SecureKeypadBuilder, CHCodeVerifier

    • onCodeRequired

      void onCodeRequired​(CHCodeVerifier verifier)
      Callback method invoked when input code is required.
      Parameters:
      verifier - indicates code verifier to input the code. This object allows the mobile wallet to display the com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.utils.securekeypad.SecureKeypadBuilder to allow the end user to enter the code in a secure interface.
